#tr.en: You alone are the sword, the butcher […]!
12. %n attā | namṣarum-ma | ṭābih[u (|) ... ]
AššNA2 i 10'. a[t-t]a nam-ṣa-ru-um-m[a] & ṭa*#-bi#-h[u?] x x x x (x)
