HuzNA1 i 23. [x {d}]IMIN-BI qar-rad la ša₂-na-an & šu-un#-na#-ta DINGIR-su-un

#tr.en: Their origin is strange; they are charged with terror;
24. %n ilittašunu | ahât-ma || malû | pulhāti
#note: @i{ilittu} here means “not so much ‘offspring’ or ‘birth’ as the stock from which one comes” (so @bib{RN117@795}).
