#tr.en: Anu, the king of the gods, impregnated Earth,
28. %n ānu | šar (|) ilī || erṣeta | irhē-ma
#note: On the motif of the frightful creatures resulting from the union of Heaven and Earth, see @bib{RN1853@196-198}.
