AššNASch5 r 3. ki-i šer₃-ri la-ʾi#-[i x x x x]
$ beginning of excerpt

#tr.en: “As one who knows not the (battle) field, will we eat the bread of women?
49. %n kī lā ālik (|) ṣēri || nikkala | akal (|) sinniš
NinNA1b i 16'. ki-i# la# a-lik# EDIN ni-ik-ka#-la a-k[a]l* sin-niš#
#note: Collation of Lambert @i{apud} @bib{RN31@Fig. 14}.
AššNA2 i 47'. [x x x x x nik-ka-l]a a-kal sin-niš#
