#tr.en: “If I should now lift up my weapons, I would destroy the rest.
146. %n kakk[īy]a | ušatbā-ma || uhall[a]q | rēha
#note: On the substantivized adjective @i{rēḫu}, “rest,” see @bib{RN358@35}, who understands the phrase in this context as “auch noch den Rest vernichten.” @bib{RN31@189-190}, following a suggestion by Deller, interprets it rather as a stative 3f plural, understanding @i{nišū} as the subject: “(Sebbene?) io alzi le mie armi e distrugga — sopravvivono (ancora).” The formulation of AššNA2, taken here in the main text, is understood here as an irrealis (on irrealis in sentences connected with @i{-ma}, see @bib{krebernik2001šumman@73-74}.
// cf. L I.5 SB "V" 41
// cf. L III.10 54
